All Folders follow the InitialCaps rule
	Except the ones containing html/css/js code like static and templates folders
	OPENi folders are also an exception

All files follow the camelCase rule

Underscores for variable, fuction and method names

InitialCaps for class names

http://lincolnloop.com/django-best-practices/

http://www.python.org/dev/peps/pep-0008/

https://docs.djangoproject.com/en/dev/internals/contributing/writing-code/coding-style/

Everyone should comment code before uploading